ðŸ« Department Section â€“ Department-level performance and contributions.
ðŸ“ˆ Projects Section â€“ Track project values, progress against targets.
ðŸ“‘ Results Section â€“ Pass vs Fail rates, average marks by subject, top 5 students in exams.


ðŸ“ Formulas Used

Performance % =Actual / Target
Results = =IF([@Actual] >= [@Target], "Pass", "Fail")

Calculates percentage of students passing.
Top N Students (via PivotTable filter: Top 5 by Marks).
Conditional Formatting
Highlight over/under-performing students.

